features: Fitment: This Ram interior LED light kit replacement package is compatible with 2019 2020 2021 Dodge Ram 1500 2500 3500 (all configurations).

Application: Map Lights, Vanity Mirror Lights, Dome Lights, Glove Box Lights, Footwell Lights, License Plate Lights. The interior LED conversion kit includes 12pcs LED light bulbs, 1pcs install tool, and 1pcs placement diagram.

Advantages: 200 lumens per bulb, 300% brighter than original halogen bulbs. Built in Constant Current IC for a 50,000+ working hours lifespan. No light color difference, all these Ram interior LED lights are designed with the same color temperature 6000K white LED chips.

Easy Installation: No error codes after installing, just plug and play. This kit comes with the placement diagram that tells you what bulb goes where and an install tool to safely replace the factory bulbs. And we will send you the installation video if you don’t know how to replace these lights.

100% Satisfaction Guarantee: All Xpismii LED bulbs carry a 2-Year warranty, please kindly contact us if you have any questions about these LEDs or installation, and we will offer you a satisfied solution within 24 hours.
body.description: Xpismii Super Bright 6000K White LED Interior Light Kit Package Replacement for 2019-2021 Dodge Ram 1500 2500 3500 All Configurations This Ram LED interior light kit includes all the LEDs you need to replace the interior incandescent bulbs. It has a placement diagram inside that tells you what bulb goes where. It also comes with a trim tool to safely replace your factory bulbs without cracking or breaking your vehicle's interior trim parts. And please contact us if you have no idea how to replace these lights, we would send you the step-by-step installation video. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Came with more bulbs than I needed…
reviews.reviewText: But that’s ok! Color temperature looks great and they were fairly easy to install. Trust me- look on YouTube for tips on replacing the two map light bulbs. It’s not straightforward and you’ll likely break something if you don’t.One complaint is that the dome light is SO annoyingly bright! I used some white spray paint on the inside of my dome light cover to tone it down to about half of the brightness and it’s so much better. I appreciate bright lights but the dome was just too bright. It’s all a matter of preference.I would have given 5 stars if the dome wasn’t so bright and there were instructions included on how to do the map light bulbs or a link to a YouTube video. Nice product overall.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Works great in my 2020 Ram 1500
reviews.reviewText: This LED light kit for Rams 2019 and up came packaged very well so nothing was damaged. Each LED works great.The brightness is as advertised and a great improvement over the factory lights. Installation was not an issue because each LED is within size specs. The back light will require some clamping due to the way its made, but this holds true for any brand LED for the dome light. Just put it in, hold it, and clamp the connectors until it is snug.I've used far more expensive LEDs in my other truck. I can't tell the difference between this kit and the other one. Only time will tell how long they last. Overall, this is a must have upgrade.
